  <title>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Help a Special Needs School Adapt to COVID Context</narrative>
  </title>
  <description>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">COVID-19 has had a devastating effect on public education in Ecuador, especially for children &amp; teens with special learning needs. Classes have been online since 03/2020, but students will gradually begin returning to the classroom in 02/2021. The Ayni Ecuador Foundation is partnering with the only special needs school in Otavalo to bring vital infrastructure, hygiene supplies and training necessary to successfully and safely integrate these special students into this blended learning structure.</narrative>
  </description>
